                        <h5>The Big Question</h5>
                        <p><img align="left" src="/images/learn-more/questions.jpg" alt="" class="circle responsive-img" hspace="20">In the Question Phase, the educator introduces the Big Question and shares some background or a short story around the question. It's important to remember not to lead students to an answer or in any way reveal what they should learn.  Big questions should lead to more questions, and don't have a single right answers.  Our site includes <a ui-sref="questions">thousands of questions</a> aligned to standards to help you get started using SOLE in your classroom.</p>
